Package: avotrex
Version: 1.0.0
Type: Package
Title: A global dataset of anthropogenic extinct birds and their traits: Phylogeny builder
Description: Grafts the extinct bird species from the Avotrex database on to the
    BirdTree phylogenies, using a set of different commands.
